# Lottie animation files for the interactive experience.
#
# Filenames referenced in src/lib/experience/scenes.ts:
#   - evening_room.lottie
#   - rabbit_hole.lottie
#   - silence.lottie
#   - shared_screen.lottie
#   - listening.lottie
#
# Until these are sourced from LottieFiles, SceneVisual.tsx falls back to a
# hashed-color gradient — the experience still works end-to-end.
#
# To swap in real animations:
#   1. Pick a free .lottie or .json from https://lottiefiles.com (filter:
#      "free for commercial use" — most cinematic illustrations qualify).
#   2. Save as the exact filename above (.lottie format preferred for size).
#   3. Commit + push — Vercel will serve from /animations/<file> via CDN.
